SOURCE: https://github.com/keystonejs/keystone/blob/main/docs/content/docs/context/overview.md#2025-04-13_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
type ImageMode = 'local';

type ImageExtension = 'jpg' | 'png' | 'webp' | 'gif';

type ImageData = {
  mode: ImageMode;
  id: string;
  extension: ImageExtension;
  filesize: number;
  width: number;
  height: number;
};
```

